THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 36202. (1) The agricultural preservation fund is created
2 within in the state treasury.
3 (2) The state treasurer may receive money or other assets from
4 any source for deposit into the fund, including federal funds,
5 other state revenues, gifts, bequests, and other donations. The
6 state treasurer shall direct the investment of money in the fund
7 and shall credit to the fund interest and earnings from the
8 investments to the fund. investments.
